				"actions": {
					"value": 1
				},
				"category": "offensive",
				"description": {
					"value": "<p>The Alp turns into a cloud of vapor, as the @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.V8wXOsoejQhe6CyG]{Vapor Form} spell, or back to its normal form. The Alp loses fast healing while in gaseous form. The Alp can remain in this form indefinitely.</p>",
